### Cadastro de Usuario
POST http://localhost:8080/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Lucas TCC",
  "email": "lucas@teste.com",
  "password": "123"
}

###

### Teste de Login (Sucesso)
POST http://localhost:8080/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "lucas@teste.com",
  "password": "123"
}

###

### Teste de Login (Falha - Senha errada)
POST http://localhost:8080/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "lucas@teste.com",
  "password": "senha_errada"
}

### Criar uma nova Task (Create)
POST http://localhost:8080/tasks/user/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Treino de Cardio",
  "description": "Corrida de 30 minutos",
  "xpReward": 100,
  "attributeType": "Agility",
  "attributePoints": 5,
  "durationMinutes": 30
}

### Listar tarefas do usuario (Read)
GET http://localhost:8080/tasks/user/1

### Atualizar para Concluida (Update)
PUT http://localhost:8080/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Treino de Cardio",
  "status": "COMPLETED",
  "xpReward": 100,
  "attributeType": "Agility",
  "attributePoints": 5
}